-
-  // Entry arguments:
-  //  rax: CompiledICData
-  //  rcx: Receiver
-
-  // Most registers are in use; we'll use rax, rbx, rcx, rdx, rsi, rdi
-  // (If we need to make rsi, rdi callee-save, do a push/pop here.)
